<C>__{kelly}
<D>__{chuck.}
<C>__{chuck}
<D>__{what do you want me to say? that i thought i'd done a great job but it all turned to shit? that i might as well have gone sailing for all the good i did?}
<C>__{kelly}
<D>__{yeah, tell me. tell me all of it.}
<A>__{he suddenly looks really tired.}
<C>__{kelly}
<D>__{you don't even know what time it is. what day it is.}
